    <item>
      <title>I feel like I have lost control over myself. What can i do?</title>
      <link>https://example.org/posts/i-feel-like-i-have-lost-control-over-myself.-what-can-i-do/</link>
      <pubDate>Wed, 19 Nov 2025 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>https://example.org/posts/i-feel-like-i-have-lost-control-over-myself.-what-can-i-do/</guid>
      <description>&lt;h1 id=&#34;success-comes-from-pain&#34;&gt;Success comes from pain.&lt;a href=&#34;#success-comes-from-pain&#34; class=&#34;heading-anchor&#34; aria-label=&#34;&#34;&gt;&lt;svg class=&#34;h-4 w-4&#34; aria-hidden=&#34;true&#34; xmlns=&#34;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#34; viewBox=&#34;0 0 24 24&#34;&gt;&lt;g fill=&#34;none&#34; stroke=&#34;currentColor&#34; stroke-linecap=&#34;round&#34; stroke-linejoin=&#34;round&#34; stroke-width=&#34;2&#34;&gt;&lt;path d=&#34;M10 13a5 5 0 0 0 7.54.54l3-3a5 5 0 0 0-7.07-7.07l-1.72 1.71&#34;/&gt;&lt;path d=&#34;M14 11a5 5 0 0 0-7.54-.54l-3 3a5 5 0 0 0 7.07 7.07l1.71-1.71&#34;/&gt;&lt;/g&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;p&gt;You’ve been wasting time because you’ve been avoiding pain.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;There’s no secret shortcut to success.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;The only thing that produces real results is to work.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Here’s the question you should ask yourself right now:&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Are you ready to work through pain and discomfort?&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
    <item>
